title: First ‘Captain Marvel’ Clip Released
body:
Brie Larson has revealed a clip from the forthcoming MCU film, ‘Captain Marvel’. It doesn’t show a whole lot but it is our first proper glimpse at the next film in the Marvel Cinematic Universe. What do you guys think? 

I’ll just leave this here. #CaptainMarvel pic.twitter.com/G8VTnnz7AE

— Brie Larson (@brielarson)
February 2, 2019

title: Mr Twonkey tries to plug his show but gets sidetracked by cheese and fast food
body:
Mr Twonkey tries to plug his show but gets sidetracked by cheese and fast food

I had a very fuzzy talk with Mr Twonkey

I had a video chat with comedy performer Mr Twonkey (Paul Vickers) on FaceTime but I could only see him as a frozen, fuzzy presence.

PAUL: That’s just the way I look.

JOHN: Where are you? Edinburgh?

PAUL: Yes, on the shore at Leith in my windmill.

JOHN: Your windmill in Edinburgh.

PAUL: Yes.

summary: Brie Larson introduce una nuova intensa clip da Captain Marvel
title: Brie Larson introduce una nuova intensa clip da Captain Marvel
body:
Brie Larson introduce una nuova intensa clip da Captain Marvel

Nella notte appena passata, Brie Larson è stata ospite da The Ellen Show, ed ha presentato una nuova clip da Captain Marvel.

Approfittando della sua ospitata alla nota trasmissione di Ellen DeGeneres, l’attrice Brie Larson ha parlato di Captain Marvel, svelando una intensa clip dal film in uscita il prossimo marzo.

Captain Marvel è diretto da Anna Boden e Ryan Fleck. La sceneggiatura è…

blog.name: super-hero-confessions
blog.title: Super-Hero-Confessions
blog.description:
Super-hero-confessions is a blog where you can submit your confessions/personal opinions about any of the super hero movies, comics, television shows, cartoons, etc.

The confessions that are posted are those that are submitted; not the opinions of the blog owners. All the confessions will be anonymous when posted. Feel free to submit photos along with your confession if you would like as well.

If you want us to see a post tag it with either #superheroconfessions or #superhero confessions
